		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3671">
						上师新著《生命这出戏》正式出版
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl02_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3671/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					希阿荣博上师的新著《生命这出戏》已经正式出版。书中除结集了上师在2012年初为弟子所作的新春寄语《生命这出戏》以外，还收集了上师新近完成的《生命的平等》、《生命的依怙》、《生命可以改写》和《同生极乐国》等尚未发表的著作。

</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3671">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3779">
						2013年6月共修放生回向
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl03_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3779/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					2013年7月16日，藏历六月初八。希阿荣博上师将在圣地扎西持林主持召开莲师法会。经过观察，上师决定在这天带领参加法会的僧众为此次共修放生回向功德。</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3779">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3719">
						《菩提洲电子杂志》正式推出
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl04_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3719/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					经过试刊，《菩提洲电子杂志》现正式推出。</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3719">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3685">
						菩提洲网站发起为期一个月的共修放生
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl05_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3685/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					为了挽救更多有情众生的生命，菩提洲网站再次发起为期一个月的共修放生。希望所有能够在这段时间参加放生的信众都可以通过网站的邮箱报名参加此次共修，待共修圆满后，我们将与大家一起回向功德。
</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3685">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3623">
						菩提洲特别推出少儿专栏“童蒙语丝”
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl06_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3623/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					“六一”国际儿童节来临之际，菩提洲网站特别推出少儿专栏“童蒙语丝”，以期为孩子们提供一个认识佛法的网络平台。</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3623">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3538">
						《次第花开》有声书出版
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl07_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3538/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					为了能让更多的人聆听到上师的法音，菩提洲网站将《次第花开》录制成有声书。现在有声书已经正式出版。
</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3538">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="vedioL DivPadd1">
			<div class="tit">
				<h2>
					<i class="ico5 pMar1"></i><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3447">
						阿弥陀佛心咒念诵共修
					</a>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="line">
			</div>
			<div class="listInfo">
				<div id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder_body_newslist1_DataList1_ctl08_Td1" class="listVd">
					<img src="../../photo/imgupload/3447/title.jpg"
						width="90" height="120" style="border-right: lightgrey 1px solid; border-top: lightgrey 1px solid;
						border-left: lightgrey 1px solid; border-bottom: lightgrey 1px solid;" />
				</div>
				<p>
					2013年4月4日，汉地传统的清明节。这天，希阿荣博上师为有缘信众赐予了阿弥陀佛灌顶。灌顶圆满结束后，在上师的引导下，弟子们举手发愿，尽快念诵阿弥陀佛心咒110万遍。
</p>
				<p class="listInfoP">
					<span class="look_btn"><a href="../../page/show/show1.aspx?magID=3447">
						查看全文</a></span></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
